### Create a new contact (valid)
POST http://localhost:5000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "organizationId": "{{organizationId}}",
  "emailAddresses": [
    { "address": "test.user@example.com" }
  ],
  "phoneNumbers": [
    { "number": "+1234567890" }
  ],
  "addresses": [
    { "line1": "123 Main St", "city": "Testville", "state": "TS", "postalCode": "12345" }
  ]
}

### Get the created contact by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/contacts/{{contactId}}

